Initiating the "Checkpoint" series on the 
@ethereumfndn
 blog - accessible, non-technical overviews of the last 4-5 All Core Devs calls with a sentiment check with what's being focused on

Had a great chat with 
@laurashin
 and 
@ralexstokes
 on 
@Unchained_pod
 !

Some of the points we discussed:
- Scaling the blobs 2x with Pectra (soon!) and hopefully 8x more with PeerDAS in Fusaka
- Why opting for a market-driven rollup-centric roadmap instead of pursuing in-protocol

EIP-7691 PEEPanEIP 143 audio podcast is LIVE!

