Tune in now: https://open.spotify.com/episode/6Tn5SjtmkUPJ4ugIlgHr5I?si=eab8d90254df4935…

how do you want to celebrate 
@ethereum
’s 10 year anniversary on July 30?

and how can the 
@ethereumfndn
 help?

I have recently taken on my new role as team lead of the Robust Incentives Group (RIG) and I am truly excited to continue pushing Ethereum forward together with our incredible team: 
@_julianma
 @soispoke
 @weboftrees
 @davidecrapis
.

A quick note on what do at RIG and some of our

Hat tip to 
@lodestar_eth
 @gnosischain
  and the Chiado testnet, they identified a bug on Lodestar before it affected us on Holesky. This helped reduce the amount of chaos and bugs to triage. (12/13)

The bug will give us an idea of how mainnet would ever perform in case such a scenario were to occur. Allowing us ample time to fix problems before they become critical. 
@ethPandaOps
 will be spending a lot of time analyzing the p2p layer performance specifically. (11/13)

EOF Execution EIP-7692, EIP-663, EIP-3540, EIP-3670, EIP-4200, EIP-4750, EIP-5450, EIP-6206, EIP-7069, EIP-7480, EIP-7620, EIP-7698, EIP-7756  Passing all tests, optimized (mostly), rebased on devnet-6
