The Ethereum community talks a lot about having better places to discuss the roadmap than Twitter, and I think leaning on what 
@abcoathup
 has started on 
@EthMagicians
 is a really good start

I’ll be stepping up as a co-lead with 
@barnabemonnot
  for research at the 
@ethereumfndn
. Researchers at the EF are some of the most inspiring and passionate colleagues I’ve found in life and I could not be more excited to support our work both inside and outside the EF.

